  "summary": {
    "en": "An upgraded 150-piece rotating-ball fort kit with ABS parts, a pink-purple colorway, and flexible indoor build options.",
    "zh": "升级版150件旋转球堡垒拼搭套装，采用ABS配件、粉紫配色，并支持多种室内搭建方式。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "Rotating ball connectors help children adjust angles more easily and build stable houses, tents, and hexagon frames.",
      "ABS parts provide a smooth, durable feel for repeated assembly and family play.",
      "The pink-purple colorway creates a softer gift style for differentiated retail and private-label projects.",
      "Recommended for ages 5-14 and suitable for home play, early education, gift channels, and OEM/ODM customization."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "旋转球连接件帮助儿童更轻松调整角度，搭建稳定房屋、帐篷和六边形框架。",
      "ABS配件手感顺滑耐用，适合反复拼装和家庭互动。",
      "粉紫配色形成更柔和的礼品风格，适合差异化零售和自有品牌项目。",
      "建议5-14岁儿童使用，适合家庭玩耍、早教、礼品渠道和OEM/ODM定制。"
    ]
  },
